<div><font class="Apple-style-span" size="4"> Run time environment of mine is Windows 7, with the unstable <span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: verdana, arial, helvetica; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); "><a href="http://www.open-mpi.org/software/ompi/v1.5/downloads/OpenMPI_v1.5.3-2_win32.exe">OpenMPI_v1.5.3-2_win32.exe</a> release for Windows, together with Microsoft Compute Cluster Pack. Additionally I&#39;m using Boost.MPI library v1.47 compiled by mingw, I write those following codes:</span></font></div>
<div><span class="Apple-style-span" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); "><font class="Apple-style-span" size="4"><div style="font-family: verdana, arial, helvetica; "><div><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#ff0000">int main(int argc, char **argv)</font></div>
<div><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#ff0000">{</font></div><div><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#ff0000"><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>mpi::environment env(argc, argv); // Boost.MPI class</font></div>
<div><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#ff0000"><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>boost::mpi::communicator worldCom; // Boost.MPI class</font></div><div><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#ff0000"><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>std::cout &lt;&lt; &quot;rank():&quot; &lt;&lt; worldCom.rank() &lt;&lt; std::endl;</font></div>
</div><div><div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="verdana, arial, helvetica" color="#ff0000">        worldCom.barrier();</font></div><div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="verdana, arial, helvetica" color="#ff0000"><br>
</font></div><div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="verdana, arial, helvetica" color="#ff0000"><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>return 0;</font></div><div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="verdana, arial, helvetica" color="#ff0000">}</font></div>
